title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Fantasy 5' game
maintext:
SACRAMENTO (AP) _ The winning numbers in Tuesday evening’s drawing of the California Lottery’s “Fantasy 5” game were:
07-12-22-26-27
(seven, twelve, twenty-two, twenty-six, twenty-seven)
Estimated jackpot: $73,000
¶ The numbers are listed in sequential order, but any combination wins.
